and I guard this humor magazine.

182
00:07:19,576 --> 00:07:21,912
Uhhhh, why?

183
00:07:22,454 --> 00:07:24,164
It's...my job.

184
00:07:25,332 --> 00:07:26,542
Why is this your job?

185
00:07:26,583 --> 00:07:29,169
I...applied?

186
00:07:29,211 --> 00:07:31,338
I'm maybe not following you.

187
00:07:31,463 --> 00:07:34,550
I think I better escort you
off the premises.

188
00:07:34,591 --> 00:07:37,553
No! No, no, no. We just want
to pitch a cartoon caption!

189
00:07:37,594 --> 00:07:40,472
Hey, Big Tina,
it's your time to shine, okay?

190
00:07:40,472 --> 00:07:42,307
[Inhales, retching]

191
