192
00:07:44,935 --> 00:07:46,478
Waahh!

193
00:07:46,562 --> 00:07:48,564
[Gulping]

194
00:07:48,605 --> 00:07:50,482
Okay, what's our plan here?

195
00:07:50,566 --> 00:07:52,359
Maybe if we eat all this ammo,

196
00:07:52,443 --> 00:07:54,319
