to make more for us.

197
00:07:54,361 --> 00:07:56,071
Wait. You can fly!

198
00:07:56,989 --> 00:07:59,074
Uh-oh!
Angle up, Big Tina!

199
00:07:59,116 --> 00:08:00,617
[Laughs]

200
00:08:00,617 --> 00:08:02,202
[Splat!]

201
00:08:02,244 --> 00:08:03,328
Uh-Oh!

202
00:08:03,370 --> 00:08:04,621
Ugh!

203
00:08:05,330 --> 00:08:06,957
You win. Fine.

204
00:08:07,708 --> 00:08:09,501
