217
00:08:42,826 --> 00:08:45,329
We can see what
the winning caption was.

218
00:08:45,329 --> 00:08:47,456
FINN: "I'm going to
write you a prescription

219
00:08:47,456 --> 00:08:49,458
for one giant club."

220
00:08:49,583 --> 00:08:50,709
Pfft!

221
00:08:50,709 --> 00:08:53,921
It's about time us young guns
took the reins.

222
00:08:53,962 --> 00:08:55,714
[Crash!]

223
00:08:55,714 --> 00:08:57,925
[Horn blowing]

224
00:08:59,843 --> 00:09:01,428
[Quacking]

225
00:09:05,808 --> 00:09:07,559
[Quacking]

226
