Hello, boys.

227
00:09:08,727 --> 00:09:12,189
Now let's roll these presses
one last time.

228
00:09:12,231 --> 00:09:13,857
[Keyboards clacking]

229
00:09:28,247 --> 00:09:31,375
[Machines whirring]

230
00:09:31,458 --> 00:09:33,335
[Hiss!]

231
00:09:34,503 --> 00:09:36,004
[Click!]

232
00:09:36,880 --> 00:09:39,508
Our very own Ble Magazine.

233
00:09:39,591 --> 00:09:41,468
And it's a pretty good
issue, too.

234
00:09:41,510 --> 00:09:43,512
We got that nice cover you did,

235
00:09:43,595 --> 00:09:47,141
