pudding jokes...

237
00:09:49,643 --> 00:09:51,103
PUDDING TROLL:
Big Tina wrote those!

238
00:09:51,145 --> 00:09:52,271
ICE KING:
..."Fionna and Cake:

239
00:09:52,396 --> 00:09:54,773
Baby Detectives
Go to College"...

240
00:09:54,857 --> 00:09:57,526
