it can't have a new dawn.

250
00:10:18,672 --> 00:10:20,174
A Blennaissance!

251
00:10:20,174 --> 00:10:22,676
Okay, boys, close her down!

252
00:10:22,801 --> 00:10:24,428
[Crashing]

253
