254
00:10:28,765 --> 00:10:31,185
No, you're right.
Can't be nostalgic!

255
00:10:32,144 --> 00:10:35,147
Man, that caption was amazing
in my head.

256
00:10:35,189 --> 00:10:38,066
Maybe I'm not
a very funny person.

257
00:10:38,150 --> 00:10:40,027
